1
00:01:02,159 --> 00:01:02,799
Your Highness.

2
00:01:03,759 --> 00:01:04,560
What a coincidence.

3
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:06,640
My dear.

4
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:08,159
What brings you here so late?

5
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,519
Who are you calling "my dear"?

6
00:01:10,359 --> 00:01:11,159
I...

7
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,879
I got lost.

8
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:13,920
Oh.

9
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,920
Then, sweetie...

10
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,560
Let me walk you back to your room.

11
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,120
This way, please.

12
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:26,680
What's "Dragon Hunt"?

13
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:29,879
The full title is Legend of the Hunter's Dragon Pill: The Attacking Coroner.

14
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,079
You drew this?

15
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:33,159
That would be me.

16
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,879
Quick, give me an autograph!

17
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:40,359
I'm a huge fan of yours.

18
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:45,120
Someone like her wouldn't have time for an affair.

19
00:01:45,719 --> 00:01:47,319
Huh? What affair?

20
00:01:47,519 --> 00:01:48,280
Just ignore him.

21
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:48,799
Hey.

22
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,519
By the way.

23
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:51,079
In my comics,

24
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,480
which character do you like best?

25
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,920
The second male lead, of course.

26
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,719
Amazing martial arts and he can braise pork knuckle.

27
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:57,920
Oh, that's right.

28
00:01:57,920 --> 00:02:00,280
I borrowed his persona for a novel I wrote myself.

29
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:01,719
A novel?

30
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,959
You write novels too?

31
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:07,959
Here.

32
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,479
The General in Love.

33
00:02:11,919 --> 00:02:13,400
I can't usually go outside,

34
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,560
so I just write for fun.

35
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,479
Don't laugh at me if it's not very good.

36
00:02:16,599 --> 00:02:17,520
Can't go outside?

37
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:18,680
Mm-hmm.

38
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,000
My husband said

39
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,159
that after becoming a princess consort,

40
00:02:21,159 --> 00:02:22,599
I can't appear in public anymore.

41
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:24,159
But King Lieyang clearly said

42
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:25,800
that you don't want to go outside.

43
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:26,759
Impossible.

44
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,719
Why would my husband say such a thing?

45
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:30,520
Really, he also said you refuse to share his bed.

46
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,439
Oh.

47
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,120
That's because he's busy with official duties every day

48
00:02:33,159 --> 00:02:34,879
and never has time to come see me.

49
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,759
He also said you're sloppy.

50
00:02:36,759 --> 00:02:38,759
My husband says he loves my casual style.

51
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,479
If I may ask,

52
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:43,319
the two of you...

53
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,319
do you get along well?

54
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,360
Of course we do.

55
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,960
He visits me every week to watch you write your novel.

56
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:51,080
Every week?

57
00:02:51,479 --> 00:02:53,120
To watch you write?

58
00:02:53,319 --> 00:02:54,120
Yeah.

59
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,319
And then what?

60
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,960
That's all.

61
00:02:58,719 --> 00:03:00,520
This is a serialized novel of a loveless marriage.

62
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,599
You're hardly husband and wife.

63
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:03,120
What do you mean we're not?

64
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,680
Tomorrow we're entering the Most Beautiful Couple Contest together.

65
00:03:14,919 --> 00:03:17,680
He probably only wants to compete with an imaginary you.

66
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,560
Consort Zhen said Lieyang City has a special wool brush.

67
00:03:20,919 --> 00:03:22,680
The lines it draws are as thin as hair strands.

68
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:23,599
I have to go buy one.

69
00:03:24,319 --> 00:03:26,000
Must it be today? It's so crowded.

70
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,199
No, I absolutely have to go buy it.

71
00:03:27,319 --> 00:03:28,039
Hey.

72
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:29,120
Let me tell you all something.

73
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:31,520
Turns out King Lieyang is a scumbag.

74
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:33,680
He actually has another woman on the side.

75
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,080
Hey.

76
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,479
Hey.

77
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:43,479
Why aren't any of you reacting?

78
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,719
I told you, no man in the world is that perfect.

79
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:54,360
He actually has the nerve to enter this contest.

80
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:58,919
If I don't expose him publicly today, I'll change my surname to Shangguan!

81
00:03:58,919 --> 00:03:59,960
Oh my, my.

82
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,680
Princess Shangguan Yan.

83
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:04,000
This is their family matter. Stay out of it, please.

84
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,919
No way.

85
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,919
Today I'll make sure the whole city knows.

86
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:10,120
The true face of this hypocrite.

87
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,919
If you don't believe me, ask the Crown Prince.

88
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:13,080
Ask the Crown Prince. Crown Prince!

89
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,120
Crown Prince!

90
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,240
Oh my.

91
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,680
Shopkeeper!

92
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,360
Where are you?

93
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,279
Shopkeeper!

94
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,319
What's all the shouting about?

95
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:31,120
Making such a fuss.

96
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,480
What do you want to buy?

97
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,160
You're the shopkeeper?

98
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:35,959
What?

99
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:36,800
Got a problem?

100
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,319
It's just that you're so young.

101
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,480
I didn't expect it, that's all.

102
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:42,480
It's all my parents' fault.

103
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:44,160
They went to watch the contest.

104
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:46,079
and left me here to watch the shop.

105
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,759
They're just bullying me because I'm young.

106
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:52,480
Small but clever.

107
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:53,399
Hey.

108
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,160
By the way.

109
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:58,480
Do you have a wool brush that can draw lines as fine as hair?

110
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,560
Yes, we do.

111
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:00,519
Hold on.

112
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:15,319
This book was written by our city lord, King Lieyang.

113
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:17,160
It's been out of stock for a while.

114
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,319
In our private school,

115
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,160
I'm the only one who has it.

116
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,560
Little girl.

117
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:26,079
Could you sell this book to me?

118
00:05:26,079 --> 00:05:26,759
No.

119
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:28,399
Give it back.

120
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,800
If you won't sell it,

121
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,920
then lend it to me.

122
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,680
Once I finish reading it,

123
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,920
I'll bring it right back.

124
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:37,800
I can lend it to you to read,

125
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:40,600
but what if you don't give it back?

126
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,959
This is a comic I drew.

127
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:51,000
I'll give it to you as collateral.

128
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:52,279
That should work, right?

129
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,800
Today

130
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:58,800
is our city's Most Beautiful Couple Contest.

131
00:05:59,079 --> 00:05:59,920
Alright.

132
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:05,560
Here is the Zixia couple.

133
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:08,920
Please show us your signature pose.

134
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:25,079
My beloved consort.

135
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:26,160
Getting nervous?

136
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:42,279
The final couple to take the stage

137
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:46,000
are the representatives from Lieyang City,

138
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:48,319
the model of a loving couple,

139
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,759
The Lie-Zhen Couple!

140
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:02,519
Bravo!

141
00:07:10,759 --> 00:07:12,879
Oh, wonderful, wonderful!

142
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:13,680
Now,

143
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:21,720
let the two of you exchange your heartfelt vows of love.

144
00:07:22,759 --> 00:07:23,560
My beloved consort,

145
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:27,000
thank you for staying by my side all these years,

146
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:29,360
becoming the harbor for my lonely vessel.

147
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:31,879
I cannot imagine a day without you by my side,

148
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,720
nor do I wish for a better life than this.

149
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:38,519
I only wish to spend my life with you,

150
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,920
and grow old together.

151
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,920
Oh my!

152
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:49,319
Now let's see their final score.

153
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,519
Oh my!

154
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:56,519
The judges have unanimously given a perfect score:

155
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:59,079
ten points!

156
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,240
Objection!

157
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:01,079
Objection!

158
00:08:01,399 --> 00:08:02,279
I object!

159
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,160
Hey, my friend,

160
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,839
This isn't the interview segment yet, not yet!

161
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,120
We at the Lieyang Gazette

162
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,519
received a tip last night

163
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,399
that Consort Zhen was caught having an affair.

164
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,319
What?!

165
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:19,519
What? I didn't, I didn't!

166
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,120
How dare you!

167
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:22,959
Why would you say such a thing?

168
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:24,199
Do you have proof?

169
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,759
Look!

170
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:35,000
Isn't this shoe...

171
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:38,080
I clearly gave it to King Lieyang last night.

172
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:40,279
How did it end up in his hands?

173
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,679
Of course King Lieyang gave it to them.

174
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:47,399
Why would anyone publicize being cuckolded?

175
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:48,679
That's because

176
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:50,320
the temptation of becoming emperor is too great.

177
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:54,360
Becoming emperor means marrying you,

178
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,120
and marrying you means divorcing his wife.

179
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,720
But divorcing his wife is such a heartless act,

180
00:08:58,879 --> 00:09:01,080
how could the devoted King Lieyang do it?

181
00:09:01,679 --> 00:09:04,519
So of course, he had to cast himself as the victim,

182
00:09:04,559 --> 00:09:06,320
then use public opinion

183
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:08,399
to openly justify divorcing her.

184
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,799
This mark is your handiwork.

185
00:09:13,559 --> 00:09:14,799
Yes, I made it.

186
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,320
This is just my...

187
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:22,519
Apparently, someone found this beneath your window last night.

188
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:25,559
My consort, how could you...

189
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,399
Let me explain!

190
00:09:26,519 --> 00:09:27,360
That shoe is just...

191
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,159
Enough!

192
00:09:30,279 --> 00:09:31,759
I gave you my whole heart,

193
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,279
yet this is how you treat me?

194
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,720
It's not like that!

195
00:09:35,879 --> 00:09:36,679
That shoe...

196
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:43,679
Stop pretending!

197
00:09:43,879 --> 00:09:44,919
Forget the contest!

198
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,080
Get off the stage.

199
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:46,879
Get off!

200
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,360
This, this, this...

201
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,080
Oh my!

202
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,879
What a scumbag!

203
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,320
Hey!

204
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,480
We're not here to play hero, don't act rashly!

205
00:09:58,519 --> 00:09:59,480
I have a scoop too!

206
00:09:59,759 --> 00:10:00,559
Hey!

207
00:10:02,399 --> 00:10:03,200
King Lieyang!

208
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,559
King Lieyang!

209
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:09,720
Who was that girl you were secretly meeting in the back garden last night?

210
00:10:09,799 --> 00:10:10,960
She was quite pretty.

211
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,159
Princess,

212
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,360
I truly have no idea what you're talking about.

213
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,320
Stop pretending!

214
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:22,000
I don't know if Consort Zhen cheated,

215
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:25,519
but I saw your secret with my own eyes!

216
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:29,120
Then you must have been mistaken.

217
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,519
Late last night,

218
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:32,399
I was reviewing official documents in my room.

219
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:34,159
How would I have time to meet some girl?

220
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,960
Everyone in the manor can vouch for me.

221
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:37,799
Young lady,

222
00:10:37,919 --> 00:10:40,320
do you have any proof to be so certain?

223
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:42,320
What more proof do you need?

224
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,120
I myself am the witness!

225
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:50,080
Well, without solid proof,

226
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,759
it's hard to convince anyone.

227
00:10:51,759 --> 00:10:52,519
Isn't that right?

228
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:05,759
Hypocrite!

229
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:07,679
Just you wait!

230
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,679
Are you here to comfort me?

231
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:29,480
I'm not here to comfort you.

232
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,120
Figures.

233
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,559
A failure of a woman like me

234
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:35,200
isn't worth comforting anyway.

235
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:37,720
How can you say that about yourself?

236
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:38,919
I'm

237
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,919
here to congratulate you.

238
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,519
Congratulate me?

239
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:43,440
Mm.

240
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,720
Hold on.

241
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,080
Look.

242
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,480
"Author: King Lieyang."

243
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:01,120
No wonder he never spent the night with me.

244
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:03,200
And was so obsessed with my novel.

245
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,960
I thought he just found it amusing.

246
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:07,559
That's not the point.

247
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,519
Look here.

248
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:15,320
Fifth printing!

249
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,759
My work...

250
00:12:21,879 --> 00:12:22,679
Mm.

251
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,799
is this popular?

252
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,399
Of course!

253
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,080
Hey,

254
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,399
my famous lady author,

255
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:29,720
would you mind

256
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:31,080
giving me an autograph?

257
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,120
Open up!

258
00:12:42,879 --> 00:12:44,759
Open up, open up!

259
00:12:46,200 --> 00:12:47,080
Come with me!

260
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,159
Hey!

261
00:12:48,799 --> 00:12:49,559
Who are you?

262
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:50,480
What do you want?

263
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:53,440
Come prove your lover King Lieyang

264
00:12:53,639 --> 00:12:54,600
is a complete scumbag.

265
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:55,960
Hey,

266
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,799
I have no idea what you're talking about.

267
00:12:58,279 --> 00:12:59,720
I don't know any King Lieyang.

268
00:12:59,879 --> 00:13:00,879
Impossible!

269
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:03,200
I saw it crystal clear last night.

270
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:04,799
Big eyes, pointed chin,

271
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:05,759
it was you!

272
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,279
Don't make wild accusations.

273
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:11,080
I'm still an unwed maiden.

274
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,799
Let me tell you,

275
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,200
just to divorce his wife, King Lieyang

276
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:17,039
would even smear Consort Zhen's name,

277
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:18,279
such despicable behavior!

278
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:21,360
You still want to defend a man like that?

279
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,879
King Lieyang's divorcing Consort Zhen?

280
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,559
Exactly!

281
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,279
Fine.

282
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,519
I'll go with you.

283
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:37,919
Another man wounded by love.

284
00:13:39,759 --> 00:13:42,759
You may have lost a single straw,

285
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:47,879
but you still have an entire forest.

286
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:50,080
That's right.

287
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:53,000
I loved her sincerely,

288
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:56,080
yet she treated me like this.

289
00:13:57,879 --> 00:14:00,000
Did I promise her too much,

290
00:14:00,399 --> 00:14:02,879
or was what I gave never enough?

291
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,960
King Lieyang, you still have us!

292
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,679
Yes, we'll always be together!

293
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:09,080
You scumbag king!

294
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,960
Here's the proof you wanted.

295
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,320
What are you doing?

296
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:19,480
Surely you recognize this witness?

297
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,320
King Lieyang, you...

298
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,279
It was them!

299
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:32,679
They forced me to give false testimony!

300
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:33,360
What?

301
00:14:35,919 --> 00:14:39,320
They said they'd beat me to death if I refused.

302
00:14:40,399 --> 00:14:41,960
Backing out at the last minute?

303
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:43,080
Hey, miss,

304
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,519
don't be rash, don't be rash!

305
00:14:44,519 --> 00:14:45,600
They were sent by Consort Zhen!

306
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:08,759
Wow,

307
00:15:14,000 --> 00:15:16,000
King Lieyang really is a responsible man.

308
00:15:18,759 --> 00:15:20,440
Are you even a man?

309
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:21,600
No,

310
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:23,759
my hand moved

311
00:15:23,759 --> 00:15:24,799
on its own!

312
00:15:29,279 --> 00:15:30,080
Are you alright?

313
00:15:32,279 --> 00:15:34,879
I told you he's no good, but you didn't believe me.

314
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,399
What's that you're wearing?

315
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,399
This is mine.

316
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,559
Didn't you say there was only one?

317
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,799
Oh, what a coincidence,

318
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,720
that's exactly what he told me too.

319
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:15,600
Oh,

320
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,720
so this is your so-called sincerity?

321
00:16:32,879 --> 00:16:33,720
It's not like that.

322
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,000
Quiet!

323
00:16:37,559 --> 00:16:38,200
Quiet!

324
00:16:38,919 --> 00:16:39,559
Quiet!

325
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:44,679
I don't know this woman.

326
00:16:44,679 --> 00:16:46,879
I have nothing to do with her.

327
00:16:46,879 --> 00:16:49,120
Besides, she already said it.

328
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:51,360
You just want to divorce me, right?

329
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:53,600
No need for all this trouble.

330
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:57,559
A man like you, with nothing but a pretty face,

331
00:16:58,759 --> 00:16:59,759
isn't worthy of me.

332
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:07,000
Fine!

333
00:17:11,279 --> 00:17:12,759
Take a good look at yourself.

334
00:17:13,920 --> 00:17:15,319
If your family weren't rich,

335
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,680
I wouldn't marry you even if your dad begged on his knees!

336
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,880
Are you even worthy of me?

337
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,839
A prodigy like me deserves a harem of wives!

338
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,160
Who would want to marry you?

339
00:17:26,559 --> 00:17:27,359
Come back!

340
00:17:27,759 --> 00:17:28,759
Get back here!

341
00:17:58,319 --> 00:18:01,319
King Lieyang got divorced!

342
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:02,839
Divorced, divorced! Come and see, come and look!

343
00:18:03,119 --> 00:18:03,720
Oh my!

344
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,559
The once-perfect heartthrob has fallen from grace.

345
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:08,119
Looks like this Lieyang City

346
00:18:08,119 --> 00:18:09,319
will be buzzing for quite a while.

347
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,799
I knew it!

348
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:13,480
How could there be a perfect man in this world?

349
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:14,559
Why couldn't there be?

350
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:16,319
There is? Where?

351
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:18,079
Something smells lovely over here!

352
00:18:18,319 --> 00:18:19,119
Hey, take a whiff!

353
00:18:19,759 --> 00:18:21,400
We just haven't met him yet.

354
00:18:22,119 --> 00:18:23,920
I don't think you'll find one in this lifetime.

355
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,720
Sooner or later, I'll meet one.

356
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,559
Yeah, right.

357
00:18:31,119 --> 00:18:32,000
Lord Envoy.

358
00:18:32,319 --> 00:18:34,279
Didn't you want me to go back and be emperor?

359
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:37,319
Let's set off right away!

360
00:18:37,519 --> 00:18:38,880
Hey, let me smell your brush.

361
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:39,960
Mmm, fragrant.

362
00:18:46,359 --> 00:18:47,160
Princess.

363
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:49,559
I no longer have a wife now.

364
00:18:50,119 --> 00:18:51,920
How about I marry you as my empress?

365
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:54,119
Your public image is terrible.

366
00:18:54,119 --> 00:18:54,720
Not a good match.

367
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:21,880
Hahaha!

368
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,519
A whole harem of wives.

369
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:32,759
I am the emperor!

370
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,319
Sister Consort Zhen!

371
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:36,480
Wait a moment.

372
00:19:37,359 --> 00:19:37,960
Oh?

373
00:19:38,359 --> 00:19:40,599
Aren't you the little girl from the stationery shop?

374
00:19:40,599 --> 00:19:41,039
What is it?

375
00:19:41,039 --> 00:19:41,839
Sister Consort Zhen,

376
00:19:42,119 --> 00:19:43,799
your books are so wonderful!

377
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:45,400
Thank you.

378
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,119
Sister Consort Zhen,

379
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,680
will you take me as your apprentice

380
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:48,880
and take me with you?

381
00:19:49,319 --> 00:19:51,319
When I grow up, I want to be like you,

382
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:53,200
a popular female author!

383
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:54,799
Actually,

384
00:19:55,119 --> 00:19:56,880
there's nothing I can really teach you.

385
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,920
You should stay here and study hard.

386
00:19:59,119 --> 00:20:01,559
One day, you'll surely fulfill your dream.

387
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:02,160
Well...

388
00:20:02,160 --> 00:20:03,200
All right.

389
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,319
But don't worry, Master.

390
00:20:05,519 --> 00:20:06,720
As your senior disciple,

391
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:09,279
I'll definitely carry on the Zhen School's legacy!

392
00:20:09,519 --> 00:20:10,759
Small but clever.

393
00:20:10,759 --> 00:20:11,359
Hey.

394
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:13,480
A guy who draws comics once told me that too.

395
00:20:13,799 --> 00:20:14,839
Draws comics?

396
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:18,880
I might know the guy you're talking about.

397
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,839
Really?

398
00:20:20,039 --> 00:20:21,319
Then when you see him again,

399
00:20:21,359 --> 00:20:22,559
please tell him for me

400
00:20:23,079 --> 00:20:24,720
that his comics are wonderful.

401
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:25,839
Okay.

402
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:26,960
I promise you.

403
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:28,119
If we ever meet again,

404
00:20:28,119 --> 00:20:28,839
I'll definitely pass on your message.

405
00:20:28,839 --> 00:20:30,599
Farewell.

406
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,480
You two are really heartless.

407
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,119
I warned you long ago.

408
00:21:17,319 --> 00:21:19,880
Don't pet stray cats on the street!

409
00:21:20,799 --> 00:21:22,480
You can easily catch a virus.

410
00:21:23,279 --> 00:21:25,119
How was I to know the cat would sneeze?

411
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:27,119
Stray cats are cute, don't blame the Crown Prince.

412
00:21:27,359 --> 00:21:29,200
If you get sick, we can take care of you.

413
00:21:29,359 --> 00:21:30,400
But if we catch it from you,

414
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,559
there'll be nobody to bring us food.

415
00:21:31,759 --> 00:21:33,119
Now that you mention it, I feel itchy.

416
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,559
You two grown men,

417
00:21:35,799 --> 00:21:37,240
how can you have no resistance at all?

418
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:39,599
Hey.

419
00:21:40,079 --> 00:21:41,480
Have you noticed

420
00:21:41,599 --> 00:21:43,160
that the guards in Chu City

421
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:45,079
have a really strange way of inspecting people?

422
00:21:45,559 --> 00:21:46,359
Yeah.

423
00:21:47,359 --> 00:21:48,160
Why is that?

424
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,480
Hurry up, hurry up.

425
00:21:49,599 --> 00:21:50,400
You, stop right there!

426
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:52,400
Take him away!

427
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,279
Hey!

428
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:55,000
Why are you arresting him?

429
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:57,599
Just like that, he was taken away.

430
00:21:58,839 --> 00:21:59,440
Hey.

431
00:21:59,440 --> 00:22:00,200
You're new here, right?

432
00:22:00,480 --> 00:22:03,039
If you've got no business here, leave quickly.

433
00:22:03,480 --> 00:22:06,000
Chu City is not a safe place at all.

434
00:22:06,079 --> 00:22:07,000
Let me just ask you,

435
00:22:07,000 --> 00:22:08,319
where did they take him?

436
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:11,640
To Prince Chu's Manor.

437
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:14,599
Our Prince Chu loves arresting people to treat them.

438
00:22:14,759 --> 00:22:15,839
Arresting people to treat them?

439
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:17,160
Yeah.

440
00:22:17,160 --> 00:22:18,960
That's a first for me.

441
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,480
Let me ask one more thing.

442
00:22:20,519 --> 00:22:21,720
Why does Prince Chu do this?

443
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,119
That, I have no idea.

444
00:22:24,279 --> 00:22:27,319
But people who've come out say

445
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:30,000
that Prince Chu's Manor is eerie inside.

446
00:22:30,480 --> 00:22:32,119
Good thing I'm in good health.

447
00:22:32,119 --> 00:22:33,319
Otherwise...

448
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:38,119
Hey, hey, hey!

449
00:22:38,119 --> 00:22:40,440
I just choked on my own spit.

450
00:22:45,279 --> 00:22:46,960
Sorry, ma'am.

451
00:22:48,759 --> 00:22:50,000
How do we get to Prince Chu's Manor?

452
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:50,799
I don't know, I don't know.

453
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:53,519
Hello there.

454
00:22:53,559 --> 00:22:54,400
I don't know, I don't know.

455
00:22:55,319 --> 00:22:57,319
Excuse me, how do we get to Prince Chu's Manor?

456
00:22:57,319 --> 00:22:58,680
I don't know, I don't know.

457
00:23:01,119 --> 00:23:04,319
Seems the people of Chu City truly fear Prince Chu.

458
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,000
At this rate,

459
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:08,000
when will we ever find Prince Chu's Manor?

460
00:23:09,839 --> 00:23:10,440
Ah!

461
00:23:10,559 --> 00:23:11,480
Oh my!

462
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,799
What are you up to now?

463
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:15,359
I need to be treated!

464
00:23:16,519 --> 00:23:17,799
Stop right there!

465
00:23:18,599 --> 00:23:19,400
Hey.

466
00:23:23,599 --> 00:23:25,000
That's actually a good idea.

467
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,279
I'll do the same.

468
00:23:29,359 --> 00:23:30,160
Ouch!

469
00:23:32,319 --> 00:23:33,119
Ouch!

470
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,440
Ouch!

471
00:23:37,119 --> 00:23:37,920
Hurry up!

472
00:23:39,240 --> 00:23:40,039
Hurry up!

473
00:23:45,759 --> 00:23:46,480
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

474
00:23:46,480 --> 00:23:48,000
Easy, easy, alright, alright!

475
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:49,000
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

476
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:50,880
I'm not sick, I'm an envoy from the palace.

477
00:23:51,200 --> 00:23:53,000
I came to see your prince.

478
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:55,119
Everyone brought in here says they're not sick.

479
00:23:55,599 --> 00:23:56,319
No, no, no!

480
00:23:56,319 --> 00:23:56,839
I have a palace token.

481
00:23:56,839 --> 00:23:57,559
It's in my bag.

482
00:23:57,759 --> 00:23:58,880
Go ahead and search my bag!

483
00:23:58,880 --> 00:23:59,480
Cut the nonsense.

484
00:24:00,079 --> 00:24:01,519
Put him in the isolation ward.

485
00:24:01,640 --> 00:24:03,000
Hey, this is a misunderstanding!

486
00:24:03,119 --> 00:24:03,880
It's really a misunderstanding!

487
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:06,119
You must be Lord Qi.

488
00:24:06,359 --> 00:24:08,480
I've been awaiting you for some time.

489
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,000
Princess Ouyang.

490
00:24:12,519 --> 00:24:13,880
You can come out too.

491
00:24:16,599 --> 00:24:18,319
Dowager Consort, you look so young!

492
00:24:19,319 --> 00:24:21,119
What's your beauty secret?

493
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:23,920
I know a bit of medicine.

494
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,400
Of course, you can't rely on medicine alone.

495
00:24:29,079 --> 00:24:31,279
You also need good living habits

496
00:24:31,279 --> 00:24:32,640
and a good mindset.

497
00:24:33,839 --> 00:24:34,640
Oh.

498
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,279
You two have come

499
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:39,200
to ask my son to be emperor, right?

500
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,000
Hm?

501
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:41,400
How did you know?

502
00:24:42,559 --> 00:24:44,400
Ever since I left the palace,

503
00:24:44,519 --> 00:24:46,240
I've been keeping an eye on palace affairs.

504
00:24:46,240 --> 00:24:47,519
Oh.

505
00:24:48,319 --> 00:24:51,000
So what does Prince Chu think of this?

506
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:54,960
Whether he wants to or not, he will.

507
00:24:57,279 --> 00:24:58,079
Uh...

508
00:24:58,440 --> 00:25:00,119
The moment we entered the city, we heard

509
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:02,680
Prince Chu is forcibly relocating the whole city.

510
00:25:02,720 --> 00:25:03,880
Why is that?

511
00:25:07,400 --> 00:25:09,880
All for that delicate princess consort of his.

512
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:13,880
Ever since he married that Lady Yu out of nowhere,

513
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:16,119
my son lost all his ambition.

514
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,720
He spends all day with that little vixen.

515
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:22,279
Thankfully, heaven has eyes.

516
00:25:22,599 --> 00:25:24,759
and let her catch an incurable disease.

517
00:25:26,319 --> 00:25:28,400
So my son studies medicine day and night.

518
00:25:33,519 --> 00:25:35,720
So the prince already has someone he loves.

519
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:41,880
How loyal and devoted he is.

520
00:25:42,079 --> 00:25:44,119
Suddenly I don't feel sick at all.

521
00:25:44,319 --> 00:25:46,039
Just let me go, please.

522
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:50,160
Want me to use you as a punching bag?

523
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:51,119
Your forehead looks darkened.

524
00:25:51,119 --> 00:25:52,880
You really need to come in for a checkup.

525
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:53,279
Move!

526
00:25:53,359 --> 00:25:54,480
You're the one who's sick!

527
00:25:54,680 --> 00:25:57,680
I'm not going!

528
00:25:59,599 --> 00:26:01,119
What good is loyalty?

529
00:26:01,680 --> 00:26:04,160
My son was born to be emperor.

530
00:26:05,359 --> 00:26:07,759
If the late emperor hadn't favored the crown prince,

531
00:26:08,279 --> 00:26:10,400
my son would already be emperor.

532
00:26:10,519 --> 00:26:11,200
Uh...

533
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:13,680
How about this then?

534
00:26:13,759 --> 00:26:15,799
I'll go persuade Prince Chu

535
00:26:15,799 --> 00:26:17,480
and see if he'll change his mind.

536
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:18,480
Wait!

537
00:26:19,200 --> 00:26:20,799
If Prince Chu becomes emperor,

538
00:26:21,319 --> 00:26:23,960
he'll surely make that Lady Yu his empress.

539
00:26:24,279 --> 00:26:25,319
Then what about me?

540
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:28,880
Don't worry, Princess.

541
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:32,200
A little vixen like her is nothing but trouble.

542
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:34,759
I would never let her become empress.

543
00:26:36,119 --> 00:26:36,960
Besides,

544
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:39,000
whether in lineage or beauty,

545
00:26:39,319 --> 00:26:41,119
she can't possibly compare to you.

546
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,799
If she ever met you,

547
00:26:43,880 --> 00:26:45,880
she'd be ashamed of herself.

548
00:26:50,119 --> 00:26:50,920
Royal Brother,

549
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:53,119
you really must take a good look at me.

550
00:26:53,200 --> 00:26:55,279
My throat really hurts so much.

551
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:03,599
The Crown Prince is the biggest fusspot among all my patients.

552
00:27:04,319 --> 00:27:05,799
You just have a little cold.

553
00:27:06,279 --> 00:27:07,720
Drink more hot water and you'll be fine.

554
00:27:08,720 --> 00:27:09,559
That won't do.

555
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,519
You dragged me in here,

556
00:27:11,519 --> 00:27:13,759
so I'm not leaving without a couple of prescriptions.

557
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:18,960
Your Highness!

558
00:27:19,279 --> 00:27:20,079
Hey.

559
00:27:20,279 --> 00:27:21,279
Chicken farmer.

560
00:27:21,599 --> 00:27:23,920
I knew you'd come to save me.

561
00:27:24,079 --> 00:27:25,160
Why would I save you? You're perfectly fine.

562
00:27:25,279 --> 00:27:26,599
I came to see the prince.

563
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:27,799
Oh.

564
00:27:27,839 --> 00:27:30,000
I've already told my royal brother why we came.

565
00:27:30,000 --> 00:27:31,000
He refused.

566
00:27:32,079 --> 00:27:33,519
Why would you refuse, Your Highness?

567
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:38,000
I'm not opposed to becoming emperor,

568
